message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper involves the segmentation of medical images using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) categories. Additionally, the use of a small number of training subjects and data augmentation techniques may be of interest to researchers in the medical imaging (cs.MED) and neural networks (cs.NEURON) fields.
